                        "ई": "ī (long vowel)",
                        "उ": "u (short vowel)",
                        "ऊ": "ū (long vowel)",
                        "ऋ": "ṛ (vocalic r)",
                        "ए": "e (dipthong)",
                        "ओ": "o (dipthong)"
                    }
                },
                {
                    "class": "reading",
                    "qlang": "default",
                    "content": "Consonants are organized by place and manner of articulation, such as gutturals (ka group), palatals (ca group), retroflex (ṭa group), dentals (ta group), and labials (pa group)."
